  <div class="blog-text">
    <h2 style="margin: 26.25pt 0cm 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 27.68px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">沙丘边建有&ldquo;沙丘柯南国际机场&rdquo;</span></h2>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">目前日本鸟取县最出名的东西有两样，鸟取的北荣町是《名侦探柯南》的作者青<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>刚昌的故乡，大量的柯南漫画迷，会来这里的&ldquo;青<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>刚昌故乡馆&rdquo;<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x4284" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">朝圣</span></span></a></span>。而另一个知名的所在，就是鸟取沙丘了，据说每年有超过<span lang="EN-US">200</span>万游客会来鸟取沙丘，就连鸟取沙丘旁原来的&ldquo;鸟取国际机场&rdquo;，现在都改名叫做&ldquo;鸟取沙丘柯南国际机场&rdquo;了，不过由于鸟取县是日本人口最少的都道府县，所以机场的利用率不高，目前只和东京班机通航，还有不定期的海外包机降落柯南机场。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0829/20180829211153053603185_910.jpg" width="757" height="24" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">图文：钱玮</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">鸟取沙丘常被宣传称为&ldquo;日本唯一的沙漠&rdquo;，资料说鸟取沙丘东西长约<span lang="EN-US">16</span>公里，南北宽约<span lang="EN-US">2</span>公里，是一个细长的海岸沙丘群。其实鸟取沙丘是由鸟取县的千代川（河流名字）入海口附近的四个海岸沙丘所共同组成，分别是末恒沙丘、湖<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>沙丘、浜坂沙丘、福部沙丘，这些从白兔海岸到岩户海岸的沙丘目前统称为鸟取沙丘，所以才有了目前可称为&ldquo;沙漠&rdquo;的规模。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image002.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0904/20180904101335672462738_910.jpg" width="910" height="500" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">翻拍于鸟取沙丘展板照片</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">游客到访鸟取沙丘，主要前往游览的区域，是鸟取沙丘绿洲周围地区，也就是原来的浜坂沙丘范围，这只是鸟取海岸沙丘其中的一部分，整个鸟取沙丘目前中间各段被河流、<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>脉、机场和城镇间隔开。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image003.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0904/20180904102606664877109_910.jpg" width="910" height="526" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">地图影像来自谷歌</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">两图对比可知，仅仅<span lang="EN-US">60</span>多年，千代川两岸，以及海岸边的鸟取机场周围，大片的原始沙地已被改造，鸟取城镇发展迅速，沙地空间被严重压缩，也只剩下鸟取沙丘绿洲周围地区，以及海岸边沙滩这些沙化区域了。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image004.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0824/20180824232023377789875_910.jpg" width="910" height="511" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">图文：钱玮</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">由于日本的海洋岛屿地质构造，让它的海岸沙地较为发达，资料称日本大约有<span lang="EN-US">30</span>多个主要的海岸沙滩，所有的大型沙地都分布在海岸线上。其形成原因是波浪的击打和推送，部分沙子被海浪和海风送上岸，产生沙丘堆积。鸟取的大沙丘高度达到<span lang="EN-US">50</span>米，蔚蓝大海前能有如此庞大的沙丘，确实景色蔚为壮观。</span></p>
    <h2 style="margin: 26.25pt 0cm 13.5pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 27.68px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">日本最大的沙丘不在鸟取</span></h2>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image005.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0904/20180904004801442473243_910.jpg" width="910" height="581" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">地图影像来自谷歌</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">不过需要特别一说的是，日本最大的沙丘不在鸟取，而是位于青森县的的猿之森沙丘，实际长约<span lang="EN-US">17</span>公里，宽约<span lang="EN-US">1</span>～<span lang="EN-US">2</span>公里，卫星图上初步估算沙地面积是鸟取沙丘面积的<span lang="EN-US">8</span>倍以上，但由于猿之森沙丘周边被用于军事武器测试之用，所以就算是日本人也没有多少人去过那里。对照卫星地图影像比较之后，对于某些国内旅游宣传材料里的&ldquo;日本唯一的沙漠&rdquo;的说法，颇觉得好笑。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image006.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0824/20180824232024327468986_910.jpg" width="910" height="511" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">图文：钱玮</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">在日本的古代，由于风沙、含盐海风和季风形成的流沙危害，让人们把海岸沙丘地叫做&ldquo;死亡地带&rdquo;。为防御海岸风沙灾害，日本历代都有进行沙地改造，建造过许多造林工程，到目前为止日本绝大多数地区的沙丘、沙地都已经固化，沙丘不再流动，沙丘周边区域被<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3725" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">森林</span></span></a></span>和植被圈围住。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image007.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0824/20180824232028118130716_910.jpg" width="910" height="511" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">图文：钱玮</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">被圈围和固定住的沙丘，由于日本多数地区降水较多、湿度大，自然环境下<span lang="EN-US">,</span>沙丘水源涵养较好，非常容易表层长草，沙漠上部会逐步被<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3743" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">植物</span></span></a></span>覆盖，渐渐形成泥土层，沙丘面积自然退化减小。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image008.jpg" alt="http://img1.lotour.net/Inspiration/2018/0829/20180829211149642803380_910.jpg" width="910" height="511" border="0" /></span></p>
    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">图文：钱玮</span></em></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">在鸟取沙丘规模退化的情况下，为了能让更多的游客充分享受海岸沙滩带来的特别感觉，能充分开发当地的海岸沙地特色旅游。<span lang="EN-US">1998</span>年开始，鸟取政府就出资清理了许多邻海沙滩的植被，让连续的沙丘面积增大，这种扩大沙化面积的做法，应该说是世界上很罕见的，也就形成了日本唯一一处可游览参观的&ldquo;海岸沙漠地貌&rdquo;景观。</span></p>
    <h2 style="margin: 26.25pt 0cm 13.5pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 27.68px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">鸟取沙丘的今日面貌</span></h2>
