    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">沙丘高地周边还有各种游乐活动，比如乘坐<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x4148" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">滑翔伞</span></span></a></span>、滑板滑沙等，还有一个沙漠<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x4142" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">露营</span></span></a></span>区，确实很有沙漠游玩的感觉。</span></p>
