    <h2 style="margin: 26.25pt 0cm 13.5pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 27.68px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">鸟取沙丘和<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>阴海岸国立公园</span></h2>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;">鸟取沙丘其实只是日本<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>阴海岸国立公园的一部分，<span lang="EN-US">2010</span>年<span lang="EN-US">10</span>月<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>阴海岸国立公园被联合国教科文组织认定为世界地质公园。<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>阴海岸国立公园西起鸟取市，东至京都府京丹后市，长约<span lang="EN-US">110</span>公里，公园保存了地壳变动和<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3742" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">火山</span></span></a></span>活动的大量痕迹，从中可以了解日本海形成至今的地形变迁和沙丘、沉降海岸等多种海岸地形，被誉为&ldquo;地形和地质<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3712" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #333333;"><span lang="EN-US">博物馆</span></span></a></span>&rdquo;。</span></p>
    <p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 15pt 0cm 0.0001pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><img src="file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image012.jpg" alt="http://img.lotour.net/zip/20110411/index_mrtu.jpg" width="6" height="6" border="0" /></span></p>
