    <p class="img-tip" style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 3.75pt 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 18pt; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0);"><em><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #999999;">图片来自<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.lotour.com/zhengwen/x3738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #999999;"><span lang="EN-US">山</span></span></a></span>阴观光推进机构</span></em></p>
